description: Deletes one or more scheduled actions for the specified Auto Scaling group.

parameters.name: AutoScalingGroupName
parameters.description: The name of the Auto Scaling group.

parameters.name: ScheduledActionNames
parameters.description: The names of the scheduled actions to delete. The maximum number allowed is 50. (string) ---

nested_items.name: FailedScheduledActions
nested_items.description: The names of the scheduled actions that could not be deleted, including an error message.

nested_items.name: ScheduledActionName
nested_items.description: The name of the scheduled action.

nested_items.name: ErrorMessage
nested_items.description: The error message accompanying the error code.
